V0512_01_00_00_0.text:
Why are ya standin' in my way?
Do you want me to crush you?

V0512_01_00_01_0.text: You have no chance to win because you're facing me.

V0512_01_00_02_0.text:
Bring it on!
I want to know how strong you are!

V0512_01_00_03_0.text: If you're half as good as you claim to be, this'll be fun.

V0512_01_00_04_0.text: I don't need anyone's permission to prove how tough I am!

V0512_01_00_05_0.text: I'll win the only way I know how - by Dueling my Duel!

V0512_01_00_06_0.text:
Stop daydreaming!
I'm your opponent, not your friend!

V0512_01_00_07_0.text:
Do I look like a RinRin to you?
My name is Celina!

V0512_01_00_08_0.text:
Will you stop staring at me!
You're freaking me out!

V0512_01_00_09_0.text: The Synchro Dimension is no match for me!

V0512_01_00_10_0.text:
I'm not running from you!
In fact, I'll chase you down!

V0512_03_00_00_0.text: This is when I'll end you!

V0512_03_00_01_0.text: You're not the Duelist I thought you were.

V0512_03_00_04_0.text: I knew I'd be in this position!

V0512_03_00_05_0.text:
It's my turn!
Just sit back and watch!

V0512_05_00_00_0.text: You're making this Duel a lot more fun than I expected!

V0512_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0512_07_09_01_0.text: This is the card I Set!

V0512_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0512_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0512_11_09_01_1.text:
My monsters!
Emerge into the light!

V0512_21_00_01_0.text: On my next turn, you're done!

V0512_21_00_03_0.text: With that, I end my turn!

V0512_21_00_03_1.text: Now give it your best shot!

V0512_21_00_05_0.text: You're Dueling better than I thought you would.

V0512_28_00_00_0.text: I expected so much more from you.

V0512_28_00_01_0.text: I'm starting to get how a Duel can make everyone smile.

V0512_28_00_02_0.text: I can't wait to Duel you again.

V0512_28_00_03_0.text:
Do you play golf?
Because your Duel has a lotta holes.

V0512_28_00_04_0.text: You can't win if there's no logic to your strategy!

V0512_28_00_05_0.text: If you rely on luck, you're not taking the Duel seriously.

V0512_28_00_06_0.text: Synchro Duelists are nothing to be afraid of.

V0512_28_00_07_0.text: There's no way you teach at Duel Academy!

V0512_29_00_00_0.text:
Argh...
I didn't know you were this tough...

V0512_29_00_01_0.text:
I lost.
Good luck in your future fights.

V0512_29_00_02_0.text:
I'll come back stronger.
And I will win.

V0512_29_00_03_0.text: I gave it my all, so there's nothing to be ashamed of.

V0512_29_00_04_0.text:
I never knew a Duel could be this enjoyable!
Thanks!

V0512_29_00_05_0.text:
I see.
You weren't just relying on luck.

V0512_33_00_02_0.text: You'll learn there's no one like me!

V0512_30_00_02_0.text:
I'm not scared of you!
I'm taking you down!

V0512_34_00_00_0.text: Practice means nothing if you can't produce the results.

V0512_34_00_01_0.text: Hey! Stop ignoring me! Show some respect for your opponent!

V0512_34_00_02_0.text:
You only Summoned a monster?
Did you forget to Set a card?

V0512_34_00_04_0.text: Luck is only for fun, and I don't play around!

V0512_34_00_06_0.text: Are you trying to irritate me?

V0512_34_00_07_0.text: Why is my heart beating so fast?

V0512_34_00_10_0.text: When this knockout gas wears off, you'll be sorry...

V0512_34_00_11_0.text:
Heard ya need a boat!
Well, I’m lookin’ for a crew!

V0512_34_00_12_0.text: They even went after people who weren't Duelists?

V0512_35_00_01_0.text: I'll take on everyone simultaneously - quicker that way!

V0512_36_00_02_0.text:
Don't give up!
The Duel isn't over!

V0512_36_00_03_0.text: Bring this Duel to an end!

V0512_36_00_04_0.text:
It's your turn.
I'm counting on you.

V0512_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Luna Light Perfume!

V0512_08_00_01_0.text: I activate Luna Light Perfume's effect from my Graveyard!

V0512_08_00_17_0.text:

Fusion Recovery!

 Fusion Tag!

Fusion Deployment!

V0512_08_00_22_0.text:

Battle Fusion!

V0512_08_00_23_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Greater Polymerization!

Fusion Recycling Plant!

V0512_08_00_26_0.text: Fusion Recycling Plant activates during the End Phase!

I activate my Spell Card!

Future Fusion!

V0512_08_00_30_0.text:

I activate my Equip Spell!

I activate my Trap!

I activate my Trap!

I activate my Trap!

I activate my Counter Trap!

I activate my Counter Trap!

I activate my Quick-Play Spell!
Book of Lunar Eclipse!
